oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hatch Show Print Air Mail Envelope
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm); Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color air mail envelope (blue and red on white) featuring the Hatch Show Print name and motto, "We Crow About Our Prompt Service." It is possible that this envelope was printed on the offset press.
